slack (0.15.0) stable; urgency=low

  * New upstream source (see ChangeLog).
        Three new options:
            --sleep SECS  (random sleep for crontabs)
            --rsh COMMAND (instead of default ssh; will replace :: syntax
                           in future)
            --version     (print version)
  * Numerous packaging and installation fixes.
  
 -- Alan Sundell <alan@sundell.net>  Mon, 14 Jan 2008 18:00:00 -0800

